<HEADLINE> Peng Zhen Passes Away </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 26 (Xinhua) -- Peng Zhen, China's outstanding
leader, died of illness here at 23:40 April 26, 1997, at age of 95.
</P>
<P>
This was announced in an obituary released just now by the
Central committee of the Chinese communist Party, the Standing
Committee of the National People's Congress of the People's
Republic of China (PRC), the State Council of the PRC, the
National Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative
