managers to 12 countries, including Britain, the US, Canada and
Japan, for scholastic exchange and research purposes.
</P>
<P>
Government efforts have been strengthened to ensure the healthy
development of the cooperation programs. Four projects in a
Sino-Canadian joint effort have been commended by the province.
</P>
<P>
Last year Hebei introduced from overseas a total of 1,153
seed strains, more than 30 sets of state-of-the-art agricultural
facilities and 895 copies of technical publications. 
