last year, in silk products, textiles, garments, light industry
products, livestock products, and raw materials.
</P>
<P>
New Zealand has 16 projects in Zhejiang, which has three in New
Zealand. Cooperation in leather goods, textiles, light industries,
and fishery is doing well. 
